Trailblazers in every sense 👏🏾 Meet Dr. Nicole Foster and Dwight Campbell, the couple behind Cajou Creamery, the first plant-based ice cream shop in Baltimore!⁠
⁠
Frustrated by the lack of clean, healthy dessert options that celebrated global flavors, they left their careers in medicine and law to build something revolutionary: dairy-free ice cream made with real ingredients and rooted in cultural inspiration.⁠
⁠
✨ Tap the 🔗 in bio or in our stories to watch their journey in our latest YouTube video!
